            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the pepper is cooking, add your <strong>spaghetti</strong> to a pot of<strong> boiled water </strong>with a generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat, then reboil half a kettle</p><p>Cook the spaghetti<strong> </strong>for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>spaghetti</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
